race.comment: NO SAVINGS (10) has put together back-to-back placings, the latest when just missing over 1900m at Traralgon when she was handy all the way. Suitably placed and anticipating another big run. PLAY IT COOL (4) had been well educated and on debut and wasn't beaten too far over a mile at Wodonga. He looks promising and kept on the fresh side, can play a leading role. YOU ROWER (3) may be the best of the remainder. Resumes and been well prepared. Well-bred and may be running into it. SIERRA SUN (2) has put a series of top-four finishes together and from this draw can continue that consistency.
